      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and it basically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition, inside and out! If you're looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken such good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
