    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive masterclass in Bavarian engineering. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its six individual throttle bodies and a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The valvetrain and double-VANOS system have been fastidiously maintained, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and a broad torque curve. The chassis remains structurally flawless, with a reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings that preserve the car's legendary telepathic handling. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral traction. This is a mechanically transparent, showroom-quality example with zero deferred maintenance.",
