    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2016 Porsche Cayman is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The Guards Red paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the finish glow. Inside, the Black leather interior remains taut and unblemished; the seat bolsters show absolutely no signs of entry wear, and the switchgear still possesses that crisp, factory-new tactile response. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive paper trail documenting its pampered history. Every seal is supple, every fluid is fresh, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
