      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a museum-grade example of the A80 chassis. At its heart lies the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring sequential twin-turbochargers and a robust rotating assembly that remains entirely stock and unmolested. Power is delivered through the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry retains its factory-spec double-wishbone configuration, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Every VIN tag is present on the original panels, and the undercarriage reflects a climate-controlled life, free of oxidation. The forced induction system holds peak boost pressure with surgical precision, and the synchros remain crisp, offering a tactile shifting experience that defines the golden era of Japanese performance engineering.",
